          sint maxime mollitia corporis magni inventore optio eius ratione quas!
          Quos nam dolorem blanditiis ut ex accusamus suscipit, aliquam nostrum
          mollitia!
        </p>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="max-w-fit text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-200 dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:focus:ring-blue-900 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 inline-flex justify-center w-full text-center">
          <a href="/flutter">Explore</a>
